《'''艾比'''》（{{lang-en|''Abby''}}）是纳特·伯恩斯坦和米切尔·凯特琳主创的美国[[情景喜剧|情景喜剧]]，2003年1月6日至3月4日在[[联合派拉蒙电视网|联合派拉蒙电视网]]共播出一期。节目围绕电视制作人阿比盖尔·“艾比”·沃克展开，她和前男友威尔·杰弗里斯在[[電視試播|试播集]]分手，但同意继续当朋友，一起住在[[旧金山|旧金山]]的[[美国租金管制|租金管制]]公寓。

伯恩斯坦和凯特琳原计划将艾比和威尔塑造成跨种族情侣，并邀请白人演员[[肖恩·奥布赖恩|肖恩·奥布赖恩]]出演威尔，但因测试观众反响不佳，奥布赖恩改演[[配角|配角]]，威尔由[[卡丹·哈迪森|卡丹·哈迪森]]诠释，剧中另外两位主要演员分别是兰迪·{{lang|en|J}}·古德温和丹吉·安布罗斯。

评论员将本剧归类为[[性喜剧|性喜剧]]或[[浪漫喜剧|浪漫喜剧]]。虽有联合派拉蒙电视网极力宣传，但节目收视惨淡，周平均观众人数仅170万，创下[[尼爾森NV|尼爾森NV]]收视率追踪节目新低。评论界对《艾比》普遍反响不佳，批评电视剧过分依赖性幽默，但波蒂埃的演出赢得赞誉。

== 构想和角色 ==
[[File:Sydney_Tamiia_Poitier.jpg|thumb]]

阿比盖尔·“艾比”·沃克（{{lang|en|Abigail "Abby" Walker}}，西德尼·塔米娅·波蒂埃饰）住在[[旧金山|旧金山]]，是虚构电视体育节目《西岸体育报导》（{{lang|en|''West Coast Sports Report''}}）栏目组为数不多的女职工<ref name="Journal1">{{cite journal | date = 2003-01-27 | title = Sydney Tamiia Poitier Tackles Racy Sports World and Rocky Love Life as Star of New TV Show 'Abby' | accessdate = 2020-09-10 | archivedate = 2018-07-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180709023225/https://books.google.com/books?id=Fr4DAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA58 | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=Fr4DAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA58&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | volume = 103 | issue = 5 | pages = 58–60, 62 | journal = Jet | deadurl = no}}</ref>。在线杂志《{{lang|en|[[PopMatters|PopMatters]]}}》的伯纳黛特·亚当斯·戴维斯（{{lang|en|Bernadette Adams Davis}}）认为<ref name="Source11" />，艾比虽是节目制作人<ref name="Book2">{{cite book | last = Terrace | first = Vincent | title = Encyclopedia of Television Shows, 1925 through 2010 | year = 2008 | publisher = [[麥克法蘭公司出版社|McFarland]] | location = Jefferson | isbn = 978-0-7864-6477-7 | ref = Terrace2008 | page = 4}}</ref><ref name="Source5">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071724/https://www.nydailynews.com/archives/entertainment/advice-upn-rid-abby-article-1.667600 | url = https://www.nydailynews.com/archives/entertainment/advice-upn-rid-abby-article-1.667600 | title = Advice for UPN: Get Rid of 'Abby' | last = Bianculli | first = David | date = 2003-01-06 | newspaper = [[紐約每日新聞|New York Daily News]] | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-09-10}}</ref><ref name="Source8">{{cite news | url = http://old.post-gazette.com/TV/20030106owen0106fnp5.asp | title = TV Reviews: 'Abby' a trite sexcom; Travel show examines jet crashes | last = Owen | first = Rob | date = 2003-01-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071716/http://old.post-gazette.com/TV/20030106owen0106fnp5.asp | newspaper = [[匹兹堡邮报|Pittsburgh Post-Gazette]] | accessdate = 2020-09-10 | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，但对任何体育运动都没有表现出特别大的兴趣<ref name="Source11">{{cite web | url = https://www.popmatters.com/abby-030116-2496237226.html | title = Abby | last = Davis | first = Bernadette Adams | date = 2003-01-15 | work = [[PopMatters|PopMatters]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071716/https://www.popmatters.com/abby-030116-2496237226.html | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。波蒂埃认为，艾比是“不会迎合他人看法和期望”的女人<ref name="Journal1" />。节目剧情围绕艾比展开，她有时想象成为别人，有时又向《西岸体育报导》主持人<ref name="Journal1" />、至交好友马克斯·埃利斯（{{lang|en|Max Ellis}}，[[兰迪·J·古德温|兰迪·J·古德温]]饰）诉说情感经历，而且忘情时往往说出一些不适合分享的细节<ref name="Book2" />。

艾比在试播集与男友威尔·杰弗里斯（{{lang|en|Will Jeffries}}，卡丹·哈迪森饰）分手，但两人都不愿放弃租金管制公寓，决定就像[[柏拉图式恋爱|柏拉图式]]室友一样继续同居。《{{lang|en|[[Jet_(美国杂志)|Jet]]}}》杂志刊登的评论认为，两人的关系既敌对又相互支持。<ref name="Journal1" />威尔是职业摄影师，对艾比仍有感情，想要再续前缘<ref name="Books1">{{cite book | last1 = Brooks | first1 = Tim | last2 = Marsh | first2 = Earle F. | title = The Complete Directory to Prime Time Network and Cable TV Shows, 1946–Present | year = 2009 | publisher = [[兰登书屋|Random House Publishing Group]] |location = New York | isbn = 978-0-345-49773-4 | pages = 8–9 | ref = brooksmarsh2009}}</ref>。他为人自私，对艾比的职业生涯毫无兴趣。剧中体现他自私的情节包括：交往两周年纪念时，他自行购买昂贵的手表；向艾比求婚时，他声称世界上没有比他更完美的礼物。<ref name="Source7">{{cite news | url = https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-2003-01-06-0301030761-story.html | title = Tv Advice: Check Out New Upn Show Abby | last = Jicha | first = Tom | date = 2003-01-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071736/https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-2003-01-06-0301030761-story.html | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | deadurl = no | newspaper = Sun-Sentinel}}</ref>部分评论将《艾比》的构思和基调与[[情景喜剧|情景喜剧]]《[[三人行|三人行]]》和《[[威尔与格蕾丝|威尔与格蕾丝]]对比<ref name="Source5" /><ref name="Source23">{{cite web | url = https://www.allmovie.com/movie/abby-tv-series-v280397 | title = Abby | last = Erickson | first = Hal | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071716/https://www.allmovie.com/movie/abby-tv-series-v280397 | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | deadurl = no | publisher = [[AllMovie|AllMovie]] | accessdate = 2020-09-10}}</ref>，[[罗伯·欧文|罗伯·欧文]]（{{lang|en|Rob Owen}}）认为本剧属[[性喜剧|性喜剧]]<ref name="Source8" />，但其他评论员大多感觉是[[浪漫喜剧|浪漫喜剧]].<ref name="Source12">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180528192118/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2003-01-06/features/0301060114_1_sydney-tamiia-poitier-john-travolta-girlfriend | title = UPN's 'Abby' won't have the last laugh | accessdate = 2020-09-10 | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-2003-01-06-0301060114-story.html | last = Johnson | first = Allan | date = 2003-01-06 | newspaper = [[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] | archivedate = 2018-05-28 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="Source17">{{cite web | url = https://www.eonline.com/news/43304/upn-tweaks-lineup-boots-hughley | title = UPN Tweaks Lineup, Boots Hughley | last = Armstrong | first = Mark | date = 2002-05-16 | work = E! News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071713/https://www.eonline.com/news/43304/upn-tweaks-lineup-boots-hughley | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="Source18">{{cite web | url = https://www.chron.com/entertainment/article/Review-Abby-can-t-get-mouth-out-of-gutter-2132268.php | title = Sex and the sitcom: Romantic comedy 'Abby' can't get its mouth out of the gutter | last = Hodges | first = Ann | date = 2003-01-06 | newspaper = [[休斯敦纪事报|Houston Chronicle]] | accessdate = 2020-09-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071713/https://www.chron.com/entertainment/article/Review-Abby-can-t-get-mouth-out-of-gutter-2132268.php | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

艾比的妹妹乔安妮·“乔”·沃克（{{lang|en|Joanne "Jo" Walker}}，丹吉·安布罗斯饰）和麦克斯都支持艾比<ref name="Journal1" />。乔鼓励姐姐忘记威尔开始新生活，麦克斯在剧中一直[[暗恋|暗恋]]艾比<ref name="Books1" />。艾比的上司罗杰·汤姆金斯（{{lang|en|Roger Tomkins}}，肖恩·奥布赖恩饰）是威尔的好友<ref name="Source11" />，为人非常[[沙文主义|沙文主义]]，经常和艾比发生冲突<ref name="Journal1" />。罗杰和威尔时常光顾[[脱衣舞俱乐部|脱衣舞俱乐部]]“约炮仓库”<ref name="Source11" />，他建议威尔同艾比重归于好<ref name="Books1" />。《[[太阳哨兵报|南佛罗里达太阳哨兵报]]》（''{{lang|en|South Florida Sun Sentinel}}''）刊登汤姆·吉查（{{lang|en|Tom Jicha}}）的文章，称罗杰是剧中装点门面的白人角色<ref name="Source7" />。[[查理·罗宾逊|查理·罗宾逊]]（{{lang|en|Charlie Robinson}}）和[[米雪·菲利普斯|米雪·菲利普斯]]（{{lang|en|Michelle Phillips}}）分饰艾比的父母，是剧中[[常设角色|常设角色]]<ref name="PostStar1">{{cite web | url = https://poststar.com/lifestyles/making-her-own-name/article_def6bd0b-7709-524a-acd4-df7c47fe2f95.html | title = Making her own name | last = Byrne | first = Bridget | date = 2003-01-02 | newspaper = The Post-Star | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071717/https://poststar.com/lifestyles/making-her-own-name/article_def6bd0b-7709-524a-acd4-df7c47fe2f95.html | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

== 制作 ==
[[File:Kadeem_Hardison_2013.jpg|thumb]]

电视剧开发期间的暂定剧名叫《艾比·纽顿》（{{lang|en|''Abby Newton''}}），[[執行製作人|執行製作人]]包括纳特·伯恩斯坦（{{lang|en|Nat Bernstein}}）、雅克·埃德蒙兹（{{lang|en|Jacque Edmonds}}）和米切尔·凯特琳（{{lang|en|Michael Katlin}}）<ref name="Source2">{{cite journal | url = https://variety.com/2002/tv/news/poitier-aboard-upn-pilot-1117866120/ | title = Poitier aboard UPN pilot | last = Schneider | first = Michael | date = 2002-04-28 | journal = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071720/https://variety.com/2002/tv/news/poitier-aboard-upn-pilot-1117866120/ | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，伯恩斯坦和凯特琳还是节目的编剧和字幕美工<ref name="Source13">{{cite journal | url = https://variety.com/2003/tv/reviews/abby-1200544182/ | title = Abby | last = Speier | first = Michael | date = 2003-01-05 | journal = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071713/https://variety.com/2003/tv/reviews/abby-1200544182/ | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《艾比》由哥伦比亚广播公司电视制作（{{lang|en|CBS Productions}}）和凯特琳/伯恩斯坦制作（{{lang|en|Katlin/Bernstein Productions}}）共同摄制<ref name="Source13" />，试播集由小伦纳德·{{lang|en|R}}·加纳（{{lang|en|Leonard R. Garner Jr.}}）导演<ref name="Source14">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://archive.is/wip/JL55M | url = http://www.thefutoncritic.com/showatch/abby/ | title = Abby | publisher = [[The_Futon_Critic|The Futon Critic]] | accessdate = 2020-09-10 | archivedate = 2020-09-10 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，与其他分集一样是在[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]取景<ref name="Source13" />。节目的配乐由里克·马洛塔（{{lang|en|Rick Marotta}}）作曲<ref name="Source13" />。

2002年，[[联合派拉蒙电视网|联合派拉蒙电视网]]宣布西德尼·塔米娅·波蒂埃（{{lang|en|Sydney Tamiia Poitier}}）和肖恩·奥布赖恩（{{lang|en|Sean O'Bryan}}）将在剧中出演主角<ref name="Source2" />。这是波蒂埃首次主演电视剧<ref name="Source22">{{cite web | url = http://www.buddytv.com/info/sydney-tamiia-poitier-info.aspx | title = Sydney Tamiia Poitier | publisher = BuddyTV | archivedate = 2018-04-13 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180413045804/http://www.buddytv.com/info/sydney-tamiia-poitier-info.aspx | accessdate = 2018-04-13}}</ref>，也是首度参演情景喜剧<ref name="PostStar1" />。她称赞节目构想是“充满幽默的沃土”，对演员的多元组成也很满意<ref name="Journal1" />。根据制作人的初步设想，威尔本是白人<ref name="Journal1" />。对此凯特琳称：“我们本希望节目中有跨种族恋情，但没打算以此作为核心内容”<ref name="Source6">{{cite news | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.nydailynews.com/archives/entertainment/poitier-making-article-1.671714 | title = Another Poitier's Making a Name for Herself | last = Petrozzello | first = Donna | date = 2003-01-03 | accessdate = 2020-09-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071726/https://www.nydailynews.com/archives/entertainment/poitier-making-article-1.671714 | newspaper = [[紐約每日新聞|New York Daily News]]}}</ref>。但因试播集的测试观众反响不佳，制作人安排卡丹·哈迪森（{{lang|en|Kadeem Hardison}}）取代奥布赖恩饰演威尔。测试观众批评试播集没有明确解决两位主角的跨种族恋情问题，多次质问“为什么不把问题解决？”<ref name="Source6" />

主演变更后，波蒂埃认为本剧仍然会通过威尔和艾比的交往体现“[[多元文化主义|多元文化主义]]精神”<ref name="Journal1" />。在她看来，美国电视剧极少出现跨种族情侣，《艾比》便是少有的例外<ref name="Source6" />。格雷格·布拉克斯顿（{{lang|en|Greg Braxton}}）在《[[巴尔的摩太阳报|巴尔的摩太阳报]]》发文评述联合派拉蒙电视网2002至2003年电视季，称《艾比》是该台在节目中增加白人演员的例证；布拉克顿指出，该剧的重点就是混血女人和白人交往。{{lang|en|[[CBS_(電視網)|CBS]]}}电视高管[[莱斯利·莫维斯|莱斯利·莫维斯]]（{{lang|en|Leslie Moonves}}）表示，联合派拉蒙电视网只是想要吸引更多的观众。<ref name="Baltimore1">{{cite news | accessdate = 2020-09-10 | url = https://www.baltimoresun.com/news/bs-xpm-2003-04-23-0304230351-story.html | title = UPN adds white characters to casts of its black shows | last = Braxton | first = Greg | date = 2003-04-23 | newspaper = [[巴尔的摩太阳报|The Baltimore Sun]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071742/https://www.baltimoresun.com/news/bs-xpm-2003-04-23-0304230351-story.html | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>

