== 播映 ==
《艾比》从2003年1月开始在联合派拉蒙电视网播出，起初定档[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]每周一晚九点半<ref name="Books1" />，是超自然题材电视剧《[[闹鬼_(2002年电视剧)|闹鬼]]》（''{{lang|en|Haunted}}''）停播后的季中换血节目<ref name="Source23" />。电视台后来将本剧改在周二晚九点档<ref name="Books1" />，紧接超自然题材电视剧《[[吸血鬼猎人巴菲|吸血鬼猎人巴菲]]》和情景喜剧《[[女朋友_(2000年电视剧)|女朋友]]》（''{{lang|en|Girlfriends}}''）<ref name="Journal1" /><ref name="Source5" />，此前周二晚九点档已经持续两年播出[[大眾文學|大众题材]]节目<ref name="Source9">{{cite web | url = https://www.trektoday.com/news/070103_01.shtml | title = 'Abby' To Debut On UPN Tonight | last = Antony | date = 2003-01-06 | work = TrekNation | accessdate = 2020-09-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071717/https://www.trektoday.com/news/070103_01.shtml | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《艾比》的播出时段收视竞争非常激烈，对手包括《[[歡樂一家親|歡樂一家親]]》、《[[24_(電視劇)|24]]》、《[[法外情真|法外情真]]》（''{{lang|en|The Guardian}}''）和《[[超人前传|超人前传]]》<ref name="Source1">{{cite news | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-2003-02-27-0302270110-story.html | title = Poitier's daughter confronts harsh reality of TV | last = Duffy | first = Mike | date = 2003-02-27 | newspaper = [[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180413045804/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2003-02-27/features/0302270110_1_sydney-tamiia-poitier-upn-sidney-poitier | archivedate = 2018-04-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

联合派拉蒙电视网以积极的推广战略宣传本剧<ref name="Source7" />，主要目标是非裔美国人观众<ref name="Source16">{{cite web | url = https://www.marketwatch.com/story/upn-introduces-three-new-shows | title = UPN introduces three new shows | last = Wilkerson | first = David B. | date = 2002-05-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071717/https://www.marketwatch.com/story/upn-introduces-three-new-shows | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | publisher = [[市场观察|MarketWatch]] | accessdate = 2020-09-10}}</ref><ref name="LATimes1">{{cite news | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2003-jan-13-fi-upn13-story.html | title = UPN's Loss Trimmed by Half, Exec Says | date = 2003-01-13 | newspaper = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180614033040/http://articles.latimes.com/2003/jan/13/business/fi-upn13 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2018-06-14 | accessdate = 2020-09-10}}</ref>。《[[德瑟雷特新闻报|德瑟雷特新闻报]]》（''{{lang|en|Deseret News}}''）的斯科特·皮尔斯（{{lang|en|Scott D. Pierce}}）发文称，电视台是“把希望寄托在新情景喜剧”和[[劇情片|剧情电视剧]]《[[白金_(电视剧)|白金]]》（''{{lang|en|Platinum}}''）上<ref name="Source192">{{cite news | url = https://www.deseret.com/2003/1/26/19700783/upn-is-still-losing-lots-of-money | title = UPN is still losing lots of money | last = Pierce | first = Scott D. | date = 2003-01-26 | newspaper = Deseret News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071739/https://www.deseret.com/2003/1/26/19700783/upn-is-still-losing-lots-of-money | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。联合派拉蒙电视网将星期二晚间节目称为“喜剧之夜”和“女孩之夜”<ref name="Journal1" /><ref name="Source5" />，但波蒂埃觉得这样把情景喜剧和剧情节目搭配播出，观众反应难以预料<ref name="Journal1" />。她还称，电视台希望《艾比》能吸引经常观看周一晚间喜剧的观众<ref name="Source1" />。

虽然电视台抱以热望，但《艾比》收视惨淡，成绩在[[尼爾森NV|尼爾森NV]]追踪的146个节目中垫底，平均每周仅170万观众收看<ref name="Source1" />。节目仅播出九集便取消<ref name="Source14" />，最后一集于2003年5月4日播出<ref name="BookFinalEpisode">{{cite book | title = Encyclopedia of African American Popular Culture [4 volumes] | editor-last1 = Smith | editor-first1 = Jessie Carney | year = 2010 | publisher = ABC-CLIO | location = Santa Barbara | isbn = 978-0-313-35796-1 | ref = Smith2010 | page = 1603}}</ref>。2003年7至8月，节目又在美国东部时间周二晚八点半[[重播|重播]]<ref name="Books1" />。《艾比》的总播出时长为270分钟<ref name="Source52">{{cite news | title = The 1,657 TV shows that spent less time on the air than the Hillary Clinton Benghazi hearing | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2015/10/23/the-1657-tv-shows-that-spent-less-time-on-the-air-than-the-hillary-clinton-benghazi-hearing/ | last = Bump | first = Philip | date = 2015-10-23 | newspaper = [[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] | publisher = WP Company LLC | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | accessdate = 2020-09-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213125828/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2015/10/23/the-1657-tv-shows-that-spent-less-time-on-the-air-than-the-hillary-clinton-benghazi-hearing/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

== 专业评价 ==
评论界对《艾比》反响不佳<ref name="Source9" />，特别是其中的性幽默<ref name="Source18" /><ref name="Source13" /><ref name="Source9" />。罗伯特·比安科（{{lang|en|Robert Bianco}}）在《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》发文称节目“令人愉快但不好笑”，批评剧中的幽默再次证明电视台过分依赖性喜剧<ref name="Source9" /><ref>{{cite news | url = https://advance.lexis.com/api/permalink/50a52533-9e5a-48e4-a8b1-aadedd11a4a4/?context=1516831 | title = 'Abby': Pleasant but not funny | last = Bianco | first = Robert | work = USA Today | date = 2003-01-06 | accessdate = 2020-02-10 | via = Nexis Uni}}{{subscription}}</ref>。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|综艺]]》刊登米切尔·斯皮尔（{{lang|en|Michael Speier}}）的评论，谴责电视剧的“约炮幽默”，“火热性爱、杂乱性爱和肮脏性爱”镜头充斥<ref name="Source13" />。戴维斯认为节目的幽默构想源头就不怎么好笑，怀疑老是聚焦艾比和威尔时断时续的恋情根本不会有理想效果<ref name="Source11" />。《[[人物_(雜誌)|人物]]》周刊的总结认为《艾比》实在是愚蠢的节目<ref name="JournalPeople">{{cite journal | date = 2003 | title = Abby | accessdate = 2020-09-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071715/https://people.com/archive/picks-and-pans-review-abby-vol-59-no-1/ | url = https://people.com/archive/picks-and-pans-review-abby-vol-59-no-1/ | volume = 59 | page = 32 | journal = [[人物_(雜誌)|People]] | archivedate = 2020-02-13}}</ref>。

《[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]》的艾伦·约翰逊（{{lang|en|Allan Johnson}}）批评波蒂埃的演出，认为节目的构想让观众很不舒服，她还没有独自撑起节目的能力<ref name="Source12" />，但也有部分评论称赞她的表演<ref name="Source5" /><ref name="Source13" /><ref name="JournalPeople" />。斯皮尔认可波蒂埃的形体喜剧演出，称赞她在面对男角色时的微妙动作和恰当语调<ref name="Source13" />。戴维斯赞扬剧中艾比的职业经历，相比之下，《女朋友》、《帕克母女》（''{{lang|en|The Parkers}}''）和《[[单身生活|单身生活]]》（''{{lang|en|Living Single}}''）就经常在情节背景中贬谪女人的职业。戴维斯希望《艾比》在女主角身上花费更多笔墨，特别是描绘她“单身而富事业心”的一面。<ref name="Source11" />《[[新闻日报|新闻日报]]》（''{{lang|en|Newsday}}''）的黛安·韦茨（{{lang|en|Diane Werts}}）批评电视剧的整体构想，但觉得节目拍出来的实际效果倒还“似模像样”<ref name="Source20">{{cite news | accessdate = 2020-09-10 | url = https://www.newsday.com/lifestyle/abby-plays-it-smart-not-silly-1.461514 | title = Abby' Plays It Smart, Not Silly | last = Werts | first = Diane | date = 2003-01-05 | work = Newsday | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213071717/https://www.newsday.com/lifestyle/abby-plays-it-smart-not-silly-1.461514 | archivedate = 2020-02-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

